race.comment: EXCEED SPEED (9) goes well for jockey Thompson who has two wins and a placing from just four rides and has been racing very consistently this time in work. Should prove very tough to hold out. NAVAL SEAL (7) has placed four from six around this circuit, draws favourably in gate three and gets the services of Maloney in the saddle. Ticks a few boxes for a race like this. CANBERRA LEGEND (8) is on the doorstep of another victory with consecutive runner-up finishes and is more than capable enough on his day. In the mix on best form. CUNNAMULLA FELLA (5) boasts a win over this track and trip and must be respected from the Heathcote camp. Can make his presence felt. BLAZEN BOOTS (11) makes some appeal with Jones on board.
